{"tid":616932,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"睡前小故事（鳩吹）（轉載）","createTime":"2018-04-04T14:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T14:59:47.000Z","uid":154783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"71b6b351d17a3d875613415379f66c48442c666a","tid":616932,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T14:58:08.000Z","msg":"殺豬的屠夫站在豬圈門口，發表了激情四射的演講：「當年狼攻擊了院子，衝進了豬圈，幾十口豬被狼活活咬死&hellip;&hellip;我們不能忘記！」豬們高聲附和道：「不能忘記！」。"},{"pid":"f9288db7c8811a3e2901290878eed88b646f807d","tid":616932,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:03:41.000Z","msg":"有一日，狗同豬講，我地院最大既敵人係老虎，老虎食豬唔𦧲骨。啲豬即刻驚到發晒蹄騰，心入面非常之憎老虎。<br />\n為咗得到狗既保護，就一直忍受住狗既欺凌。終於有一日，有隻豬話：「咁多年一隻老虎都唔見，反而係你係到恰鳩我地！」隻狗就話：「我地要時刻警惕老虎來犯！知道無？你個豬奸！」"},{"pid":"8fc8e2c28f034963a68193e94c6e3a1ec34a811e","tid":616932,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:11:00.000Z","msg":"好幸福，動物農莊啲動物好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28f95c61d31e3b550b0bae9e5b07888e6862ac9","tid":616932,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:15:24.000Z","msg":"爺爺屙咗督屎叫狼食咗去，狼唔制，又叫咗狗嚟，狗唔單止食咗去，仲幫爺爺奶返乾淨個屎眼。<br />\n於是乎，爺爺趕咗狼出家園。無咗狼，狗詡住爺爺既庇護，係園入面作威作福，做齊晒所有下作既勾當。<br />\n有動物問狗：「你真係唔驚爺爺收拾你？」狗笑住答：「嘻嘻，只要一日爺爺屎忽到仲有屎，我一日都唔會有事！」<br />\n<br />\n譯廣東話好似怪怪地咁。"},{"pid":"6318008547fb516a0d8899e2d09a830c15da6f81","tid":616932,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:18:52.000Z","msg":"一群豬係豬圈入面興奮咁議論：「聽講主人又搞到把好巴閉既殺豬刀！」「威水！」「勁抽！」「犀飛利！」「睇下以後邊個夠薑恰鳩我地！」"},{"pid":"94ba549773871ed642d8765cbbcbe15f54c8c45f","tid":616932,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:23:27.000Z","msg":"有隻豬走嚟同狗講：「狗哥！你可唔可以同爺爺反映下，我啲豬囝餓到就嚟死啦！」狗衝上去，鎮壓控制咗隻豬，揞住佢把口：「咪嘈啦，園入面開緊會，商量緊點解決動物生活問題架啦。」"},{"pid":"b89e9b8ea6d60f9504497e61a64ccae354a736c5","tid":616932,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:28:23.000Z","msg":"一車豬喺被送往屠宰場既路上。<br />\n其中一隻搏命掙扎嘶叫，搞到成車豬都好唔啹。於是乎，其他豬就鬧佢：「嘈生晒！安安靜靜唔得咩？一間架車反咗對大家有咩著數？」"},{"pid":"00d88704459ebe5f8a827d9577fa7a4de49738b3","tid":616932,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T17:50:50.000Z","msg":"無人睇故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301e823ec31523e6c525a452a592c32f1ecf8d25","tid":616932,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T18:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc18039fccf3fea8764d9bfdd32d9c4d3efa8a19","tid":616932,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"幾有深度，more<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08610c6c7a2416bc817fc2448ae6c56c99e3c597","tid":616932,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc18039fccf3fea8764d9bfdd32d9c4d3efa8a19","tid":616932,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"幾有深度，more<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:48:37.000Z","msg":"無人睇"},{"pid":"9797ffe4184bcceed392157309849f5047ae7f63","tid":616932,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08610c6c7a2416bc817fc2448ae6c56c99e3c597","tid":616932,"uid":154783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc18039fccf3fea8764d9bfdd32d9c4d3efa8a19","tid":616932,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"幾有深度，more<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:48:37.000Z","msg":"無人睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:48:59.000Z","msg":"我呀，我想睇呀"},{"pid":"98d1acb39180782c02efc64d57297daa1f723b49","tid":616932,"uid":8726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08610c6c7a2416bc817fc2448ae6c56c99e3c597","tid":616932,"uid":15